            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, carefully add the <strong>pizza base<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>to the pan<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>, pushing the dough out to the edge to help shape the crust</p><p>Tip: To pick up the pizza dough, gently flip it over the back of your hand to stop it ripping!</p><p>Add 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1/4]</span> of the <strong>tomato sauce </strong>to each pizza and spread it evenly with the back of a spoon (be careful of the hot pan!)</p><p>Cook the <strong>pizza base<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> for 3-4 min or until the crust has started to puff up, then remove the heated tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and slide the pizza base<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]<strong> </span></strong>onto the tray</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1595496139934-x200.jpg",
