    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>rocket </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix it all together – this is your<strong> rocket salad</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> over the pizzas and serve the<strong> rocket salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
